# subscript(_:)

**Instance Subscript**

Creates a subset of the table given a range of rows.

## Declaration

```swift
subscript(slice: Range<Int>) -> MLDataTable { get }
```

## Parameters

- **slice**: A range of integers indicating which rows to include in the new data table.

## Return Value

A new data table.
